trans-unit.source: Renders the contained 3-D content within the 2-D layout bounds of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Viewport3D" /> element.
trans-unit.target: Renderiza o conteúdo 3D contido dentro dos limites de layout 2D do elemento <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Viewport3D" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Viewport3D> element renders 3-D content while providing features consistent with <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement> objects including 2-D layout, clipping, and input events.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Viewport3D> elemento renderiza 3D conteúdo fornecendo recursos consistentes com <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement> objetos incluindo layout 2D, corte e eventos de entrada.

trans-unit.source: When this element is included as the content of a layout element like <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Canvas>, specify the size of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Viewport3D> by setting its <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Height%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Width%2A> properties (inherited from <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement>).
trans-unit.target: Quando esse elemento é incluído como o conteúdo de um elemento de layout como <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Canvas>, especifique o tamanho do <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Viewport3D> definindo seu <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Height%2A> e <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Width%2A> propriedades (herdado de <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement>).

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Viewport3D> extends 2-D hit testing into the 3-D scene by extruding the 2-D hit test point into a 3-D ray.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Viewport3D> estende 2D teste de clique na cena 3D por extrusão o ponto de teste de hit 2D em um raio 3D.

trans-unit.source: Call the <xref:System.Windows.Media.VisualTreeHelper.HitTest%2A> method to return detailed hit result information about the hit visual, model, mesh, and point of intersection.
trans-unit.target: Chamar o <xref:System.Windows.Media.VisualTreeHelper.HitTest%2A> método para retornar detalhadas ocorrências resultado informações sobre o visual de ocorrência, modelo, malha e o ponto de interseção.

trans-unit.source: On [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_whistler](~/includes/tlasharptla-whistler-md.md)], if the display color quality is not set to 32-bit or 16-bit, the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Viewport3D> might not render as expected.
trans-unit.target: Em [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_whistler](~/includes/tlasharptla-whistler-md.md)], se a qualidade de cor de exibição não está definida como 32 bits ou 16 bits, o <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Viewport3D> podem não ser renderizadas como esperado.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Viewport3D" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Viewport3D" />.

trans-unit.target: O tamanho que <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Viewport3D" /> assumirá.

trans-unit.source: Causes the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Viewport3D" /> to arrange its visual content to fit a specified size.
trans-unit.target: Faz com que o <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Viewport3D" /> organize seu conteúdo visual para se ajustar a um tamanho especificado.

trans-unit.source: The final size of the arranged <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Viewport3D" />.
trans-unit.target: O tamanho final do <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Viewport3D" /> organizado.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a camera object that projects the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_3d](~/includes/tlasharptla-3d-md.md)] contents of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Viewport3D" /> to the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_2d](~/includes/tlasharptla-2d-md.md)] surface of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Viewport3D" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define um objeto de câmera que projeta o conteúdo [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_3d](~/includes/tlasharptla-3d-md.md)] do <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Viewport3D" /> para a superfície [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_2d](~/includes/tlasharptla-2d-md.md)] do <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Viewport3D" />.

trans-unit.source: The camera that projects the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_3d](~/includes/tlasharptla-3d-md.md)] contents to the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_2d](~/includes/tlasharptla-2d-md.md)] surface.
trans-unit.target: A câmera que projeta o conteúdo [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_3d](~/includes/tlasharptla-3d-md.md)] na superfície [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_2d](~/includes/tlasharptla-2d-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: This property represents the viewing projection of the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_3d](~/includes/tla2sharptla-3d-md.md)] scene.
trans-unit.target: Esta propriedade representa a projeção de exibição do [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_3d](~/includes/tla2sharptla-3d-md.md)] cena.
